<p style="text-align: center;"><img height="300" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Facilities Management/Security and Safety/Dec 10 winter crash.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="400" />Please be careful when traveling - and don't be in a hurry!<a href="http://www.udot.utah.gov/main/f?p=100:pg:2232045122478766::::V,T:,1673" target="_blank"></a></p>
